      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DADDY COOL (1) boasts a strong record this course with two wins and two minors from six tries. Below best last time at Sale (24.83) in a Free For All, finishing a 7 length fourth. Expected to be in the finish. GALLOPING HAPPY (2) broke well and quickly mustered speed to win over the 390m at Ballarat two runs back then settled forward again when finishing second at Geelong last start. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Can feature again. PLAY LAB (8) missed the frame latest when sixth at Sale (24.86) but scored three back at Shepparton (22.10). Has a good record here at this journey. Can do much better this time. PAW QUARK (3) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
